Welcome to the Port of Choice!
Morale, Welfare, and Recreation (MWR) for Naval Station Mayport in Jacksonville, FL provides a variety of programs and activities for the local community. Our programs are available to DoD ID cardholders and to MWR Card members.
Mission
Morale, Welfare, and Recreation (MWR) delivers programs, products, and services that support Fleet and Family Readiness and enhance the quality of life for the community at Naval Station Mayport.
Vision
To be the Port of Choice by fulfilling the needs, wants, and desires of our customers.
Values
Superior Service
Value Creation
Willingness to Evolve
Culture of Commitment

Deployed Forces Support
The Deployed Forces Support program provides administrative support and fitness equipment for homeported ships. This department also coordinates homecomings for ships and conducts briefs for visiting ships to inform Sailors of recreation and tourism opportunities.
